                <note rend="inline" type="source">824.01/48: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Bolivia</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Muccio</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">La Paz</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1936-05-30T18:00:00-04:00"
                            >May 30, 1936—6 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received 7:20 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>32. Department’s telegram May 30, 10 a.m. Note delivered May 30, 5 p.m.</p>
                <p>Repeated to Buenos Aires.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Muccio</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
